ig Kerstfeest en gelukkig Nieuwjaar", "Nord-samisk: Mii s\u00e1vvat didjiide buriid juovllaid ja lihkola\u0161 o\u0111\u0111a jagi", "Polsk: Weso\u0142ych \u015awi\u0105t i Szcz\u0119\u015bliwego Nowego Roku!", "Russisk: \u0421 \u0420\u043e\u0436\u0434\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e\u043c \u0438 \u0441 \u041d\u043e\u0432\u044b\u043c \u0413\u043e\u0434\u043e\u043c!", "Spansk: Feliz Navidad y pr\u00f3spero a\u00f1o nuevo", "Svensk : God jul och gott nytt \u00e5r", "Tysk: Frohe Weihnachten und ein gl\u00fcckliches neues Jahr", "Ungarsk : Kellemes Kar\u00e1csonyi \u00dcnnepeket \u00e9s Boldog \u00daj \u00c9vet"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "64e0756bef536b39e888647a76ec29fef841f61a8779ce246ec74dd713230b5e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-12-27T15:08:30.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Godt nytt: du kan si \u00abgod jul\u00bb helt til du b\u00f8r si \u00abgodt nytt \u00e5r\u00bb!"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13984157.ece/1pcts9/ALTERNATES/w980-default/jul.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/97707501b91c8b613575f5b84d38ff4eea929bfe.jpg?58fbc144"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["\u00abGod jul\u00bb eller \u00abgledelig jul\u00bb? -adressa.no", "Fra m\u00f8blerte vestkanthjem", "Husk sm\u00e5 bokstaver", "J\u00f3l, geol, jiuleis og joulu", "Happy Christmas (for our international friends)"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "97707501b91c8b613575f5b84d38ff4eea929bfe"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "